  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scopes 工作范围</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>1. Teach Classes Across Various Levels 教授不同级别班级的课程</p>\n<p>2. Serve As The Class Teacher Handling All Matters Related To Children’s Welfare And Daily Routine Care 负责与儿童福利和日常照护相关的事项</p>\n<p>3. Assist Other Teachers And Support Other Classes When Needed 按需协助其他教师，并支援其他班级的教学工作</p>\n<p>4. Prepare Lesson Plans For The Class/Classes In Charge 为所负责的班级/课程制定与准备教学计划</p>\n<p>5. Possess Strong Communication Skills And Effective Classroom Management Abilities 具备良好的沟通能力及有效的课堂管理技巧</p>\n<p>6. Work 44-48 Hours Per Week 每周工作 44–48 小时</p>\n<p>7. Salary Will Be Based On Experience And Qualifications 薪资将根据经验与资历评定</p>",
